e suggest that pop III stars alone cannot be\nresponsible for the abundance ratios in these objects and that intermediate\nmass pop II stars must have played an important role especially in enriching\nDLAs in nitrogen.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 23 Feb 2005 18:28:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 28 Apr 2005 17:06:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-10"}
