ar wormhole geometry. These phantom energy traversable wormholes have\nfar-reaching physical and cosmological implications. For instance, an advanced\ncivilization may use these geometries to induce closed timelike curves,\nconsequently violating causality.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 23 Feb 2005 16:35:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 6 Apr 2005 13:25:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-11-26"}
